away?"
"Exactly,
captain.
I
thought
the
post
would
suit
you.
Will
you
favour
Caroline
so
far
as
to
be
her
guest
for
one
night?
Will
you
stay
here
instead
of
going
back
to
Fieldhead?"
"And
what
will
Mrs.
Pryor
do?
she
expects
me
home."
"I
will
send
her
word.
Come,
make
